author: Victoria Hernandez
title: Curren$y Shares 1st Project of 2017: Jet Life Crew's "The Jetlanta EP"
text:
1 
Curren$y is not leaving his work ethic behind in 2016. He opens this year with his Jet Life Crew for The Jetlanta EP after releasing 12 projects in 12 months . 
The Jetlanta EP showcases the talents of Corner Boy P and T.Y. and is made up of six tracks with production from Don Cannon, Sledgren and Purpz of 808 Mafia. 
Corner Boy P and T.Y. appeared on a few of the Jet Life Recordings boss’s projects last year, including 9/30 and 11/30 . 
Curren$y was a runner-up for HipHopDX’s “We Working” Artist of the Year in 2016 for his incredible output of music.
